SIMPLE: oversight
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oversight
<hw>O"ver*sight`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Watchful care; superintendence; general supervision.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An overlooking; an omission; an error.</def>
<rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Escape from an overlooked peril.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧His fool-happy <xex>oversight</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Superintendence; supervision; inspection;
overlooking; inadvertence; neglect; mistake; error; omission.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>oversimplified</ent>⟦br⟧
